note bottom of P_ADMIN
  Routes types : /api/admin, /api/admin/super-app,
  /api/admin/stars, /api/admin/ai-engine,
  /api/admin/business-intelligence
end note

note bottom of P_WALLET
  Routes types : /api/wallet, /api/payments,
  /api/coins, /api/microcredit, /api/tontines,
  /api/savings, /api/virtual-cards, /api/utility-bills,
  /api/airtime, /api/bills, /api/payment-request
end note

@enduml
